OL,3,COctober 7: What's changed for British
OL,4,CJews and Muslims in the last year?
OL,6,FBoth antisemitic and Islamophobic hate
OL,7,Fcrime incidents have soared. For
OL,8,FBritish Jews, 2023 was the worst year
OL,9,Ffor UK antisemitism since records
OL,10,Fbegan 40 years ago, according to the
OL,11,FCommunity Security Trust, and for
OL,12,FMuslims the highest in 14 years
OL,13,Faccording to charity Tell Mama - and
OL,14,Fthat's only counting the crimes
OL,15,Factually reported.
OL,17,FITV News reporters Sam Holder and
OL,18,FShehab Khan spent time with Jewish and
OL,19,FMuslim communities respectively to
OL,20,Fhear about how their lives have
OL,21,Fchanged in the last year.
